<Defs>

  <ThingDef ParentName="BasePawn">
    <defName>Control</defName>
    <label>Controller</label>
    <description>The controller is fighting against your brain. Not in the sense that he thinks, but in the sense that he is a telepath. When you hunt him, you use cover more often. The controller must see you, otherwise he will not be able to influence you. And one more thing: He cannot run at all. So, if you really need to, try to treat him to a grenade.</description>
